Install instructions

From source

To install srvdir from source, you need to have Go (http://golang.org)
installed, and run from terminal:

    % go get github.com/fsouza/srvdir

Make sure $GOPATH/bin is your path.

Binary distributions

srvdir is also distributed in binary format:

    darwin:
        amd64: https://github.com/downloads/fsouza/srvdir/srvdir_darwin_amd64.tar.gz
        386: https://github.com/downloads/fsouza/srvdir/srvdir_darwin_386.tar.gz

    linux:
        amd64: https://github.com/downloads/fsouza/srvdir/srvdir_linux_amd64.tar.gz
        386: https://github.com/downloads/fsouza/srvdir/srvdir_linux_386.tar.gz
